# REPL_L2

1. Setup replication on both site.
2. When replicate is progressing, do the following operation against on primary site, or standby site:
Continuously 
create/delete volumes;
enable/disable volumes;
resize volumes
bonnie running

Note: the replicated acfs fs was not resided on the above volumes.

Variant:
1. Setup replication on both site.
2. When replicate is progressing, do the following operation against on primary fs, or standby fs:
Continuously 
Resize/fsck/snap
Continuously 
add/drop disk;
online/offline disk;
